# Model Configuration Presets (used by individual flows)
# These are defined in src/aws/bedrock/flow-base.ts and don't need environment variables
# Each flow selects the appropriate preset based on its requirements:
#   - SIMPLE: Haiku, temp 0.3, 2K tokens (bio, sentiment)
#   - BALANCED: Sonnet 3.5, temp 0.5, 4K tokens (FAQs, market updates)
#   - CREATIVE: Sonnet 3.5, temp 0.7, 4K tokens (social media, video scripts)
#   - LONG_FORM: Sonnet 3.5, temp 0.6, 8K tokens (blog posts, research)
#   - ANALYTICAL: Sonnet 3.5, temp 0.2, 4K tokens (NAP audit, competitors)
#   - CRITICAL: Opus, temp 0.1, 4K tokens (high-accuracy tasks)

